[{"id":"x-cookies","name":"X Cookies","yield":null,"ingredients":[{"qty":"500","unit":"g","item":"All-purpose flour","prep":null},{"qty":"160","unit":"ml","item":"Sugar","prep":null},{"qty":"5","unit":"ml","item":"Baking powder","prep":null},{"qty":"5","unit":"ml","item":"Salt","prep":null},{"qty":"240","unit":"ml","item":"Butter","prep":null},{"qty":"1","unit":null,"item":"Egg","prep":null},{"qty":"350","unit":"g","item":"Dried figs","prep":null},{"qty":"120","unit":"ml","item":"Chopped almonds","prep":null},{"qty":"80","unit":"ml","item":"Apricot preserves","prep":null},{"qty":"60","unit":"ml","item":"Golden raisins","prep":null},{"qty":"60","unit":"ml","item":"Chopped candied orange peel","prep":null},{"qty":"80","unit":"ml","item":"Semisweet chocolate chips","prep":null},{"qty":"60","unit":"ml","item":"Dark rum","prep":null},{"qty":"2.5","unit":"ml","item":"Ground cinnamon","prep":null},{"qty":"1","unit":null,"item":"Egg","prep":"beaten"},{"qty":"30","unit":"ml","item":"Milk","prep":null},{"qty":"120","unit":"ml","item":"Confectioners' sugar for dusting","prep":null}],"instructions":["In a medium bowl, stir together the flour, sugar, baking powder, and salt. Cut in butter using a pastry blender, or pinching between your fingers. Add egg, and mix until a dough forms. It may take a couple of minutes of mixing. When the dough starts to hold together, turn it out onto a floured surface and knead briefly. Shape dough into a long roll, wrap, and set aside.","Place the figs, almonds, apricot preserves, raisins, orange peel, chocolate, rum, and cinnamon into a food processor or blender. Process until finely chopped. If the fruit is hard, it may be soaked in boiling water to soften for 15 minutes before processing.","Preheat the oven to 177\u00b0C (175 degrees C). In a small bowl, mix together the remaining egg and milk to make an egg wash.","Divide dough into 12 pieces. On a lightly floured surface, roll each piece out into a 3x12 inch rectangle. Brush the strips of dough lightly with egg wash. Place a strip of the fruit mixture lengthwise down the center of each piece of dough, and fold the edges over. Roll gently to seal. This will make the filled tube of dough a little bit longer. Cut each tube into 3 inch pieces. Make a one inch long slit with a knife down the center of each cut end. Spread the ends out to form an X shape. Place cookies 2 inches apart onto lightly greased cookie sheets.","Bake for 15 to 20 minutes in the preheated oven, or until the edges are golden. Allow cookies to cool on the tray for at least 5 minutes, so they will not be too delicate, before removing to wire racks to cool completely. Dust with confectioners' sugar when cool."],"dietary_tags":["vegetarian","gluten-free"],"category":"Dessert","cuisine":"Italian","source":"allrecipes","source_url":"https://www.allrecipes.com/recipe/50534/x-cookies/","protein":["egg"]},{"id":"xau-xau-rice-teleculinaria","name":"Xau Xau Rice","original_name":"Arroz xau xau","original_language":"pt","yield":"4","ingredients":[{"qty":null,"unit":null,"item":"300 g  arroz","prep":null},{"qty":null,"unit":null,"item":"2  ovos m","prep":null},{"qty":null,"unit":null,"item":"1  pimento vermelho","prep":null},{"qty":null,"unit":null,"item":"100 g  ervilhas","prep":null},{"qty":null,"unit":null,"item":"100 g  bacon aos cubos","prep":null},{"qty":null,"unit":null,"item":"600 ml  \u00e1gua","prep":null},{"qty":null,"unit":null,"item":"4 colheres (sopa)  molho de soja","prep":null},{"qty":null,"unit":null,"item":"2 colheres (sopa)  \u00f3leo","prep":null},{"qty":null,"unit":null,"item":"Q.b.  sal e pimenta","prep":null}],"instructions":["Num tacho, coloque a \u00e1gua temperada com sal e deixe ferver. Adicione o arroz, mexa, tape o tacho e deixe cozinhar, durante 10 minutos. Retire do lume, escorra e reserve.","Numa ta\u00e7a, bata os ovos. Leve uma frigideira ao lume, coloque 1 colher (sopa) de \u00f3leo, adicione os ovos batidos, deixe cozinhar, mexendo sempre, at\u00e9 os ovos ficarem cozinhados. Retire do lume e reserve.","Noutra frigideira, junte o restante \u00f3leo e salteie o bacon, adicione o pimento, lavado, limpo de sementes e cortado em cubos, e as ervilhas. Tempere com sal e pimenta, mexa e deixe cozinhar durante 5 minutos.","De seguida, acrescente o arroz e os ovos mexidos, saltei tudo muito bem, junte o molho de soja e envolva. Retire do lume e sirva de seguida."],"dietary_tags":[],"category":null,"cuisine":"Portuguese","source":"teleculinaria","protein":["pork","egg"],"tags":[]},{"id":"xerotigana-of-crete-argiro","name":"Xerotigana Of Crete","original_name":"\u039e\u03b5\u03c1\u03bf\u03c4\u03ae\u03b3\u03b1\u03bd\u03b1 \u039a\u03c1\u03ae\u03c4\u03b7\u03c2","original_language":"el","yield":null,"ingredients":[{"qty":null,"unit":null,"item":"1/4 \u03c6\u03bb.\u03b5\u03bb\u03b1\u03b9\u03cc\u03bb\u03b1\u03b4\u03bf","prep":null},{"qty":null,"unit":null,"item":"1\u00bc \u03c6\u03bb.\u03bd\u03b5\u03c1\u03cc","prep":null},{"qty":null,"unit":null,"item":"2 \u03ba.\u03c3.\u03c1\u03b1\u03ba\u03ae","prep":null},{"qty":null,"unit":null,"item":"\u039b\u03af\u03b3\u03b5\u03c2\u03c3\u03c4\u03b1\u03b3\u03cc\u03bd\u03b5\u03c2 \u03c7\u03c5\u03bc\u03cc \u03bb\u03b5\u03bc\u03bf\u03bd\u03b9\u03bf\u03cd","prep":null},{"qty":null,"unit":null,"item":"\u0391\u03bb\u03b5\u03cd\u03c1\u03b9 \u03c3\u03ba\u03bb\u03b7\u03c1\u03cc \u03cc\u03c3\u03bf \u03c3\u03b7\u03ba\u03ce\u03c3\u03b5\u03b9 \u03c0\u03b5\u03c1\u03af\u03c0\u03bf\u03c5 4 \u03c6\u03bb.","prep":null},{"qty":null,"unit":null,"item":"\u039b\u03af\u03b3\u03bf\u03ad\u03be\u03c4\u03c1\u03b1 \u03b1\u03bb\u03b5\u03cd\u03c1\u03b9 \u03b3\u03b9\u03b1 \u03c4\u03bf \u03ac\u03bd\u03bf\u03b9\u03b3\u03bc\u03b1 \u03c6\u03cd\u03bb\u03bb\u03bf\u03c5","prep":null},{"qty":null,"unit":null,"item":"\u0395\u03bb\u03b1\u03b9\u03cc\u03bb\u03b1\u03b4\u03bf \u03b3\u03b9\u03b1 \u03c4\u03bf \u03c4\u03b7\u03b3\u03ac\u03bd\u03b9\u03c3\u03bc\u03b1","prep":null},{"qty":null,"unit":null,"item":"\u03a3\u03b9\u03c1\u03cc\u03c0\u03b9 \u03